snippet.title: Dr. Hollowed
snippet.description:
We Are Two People Working on The Channel including Story Gathering, Editing, Narrations, Background Images and voices, Thumbnails and Uploading. 
We do it all by ourself
Our Narrations mostly cover AskReddit, NoSleep, LetsNotMeet, and Paranormal Parts of Reddit; all stories taken and narrated with permission from the author or Copyright Free content.
Remember, "Everything is true, even if it is not"
